Review Text:
Ordered 1 cheese chicken shawarma and 1 regular chicken shawarma. Shawarmas are tasty no doubt in that. But cheese shawarma didn't have cheese in it, atleast I could see the difference. Regular shawarma had way too many onions and cucumber pieces. Even chicken quantity was less in both of them.
I am giving 4 star just on the basis of shawarma's taste. Otherwise other factors just deserve 2-3 stars.
i wanted a non spicy shawarma and it came out to be super spicy.. might have to throw it now
